INSERT INTO votes_count (object_id, object_type, space_id, upvotes, downvotes)
                VALUES ($1, $2, $3, $4, $5)
                ON CONFLICT (object_id, object_type, space_id)
                DO UPDATE SET 
                    upvotes = EXCLUDED.upvotes,
                    downvotes = EXCLUDED.downvotes
